summary: In the 39th match of IPL 2024, Lucknow Super Giants (LSG) emerged victorious over Chennai Super Kings (CSK). name: Columbia University
summary: Recent protests have erupted at several universities across the United States in response to the ongoing conflict in Gaza. Protesters at Columbia University faced arrests and police intervention as they chanted insults outside the institution. Yale University also saw arrests as 47 student demonstrators were detained for trespassing. Columbia University student Isra Hirsi, daughter of Congresswoman Ilhan Omar, discussed the arrests and suspension of a Barnard College student involved in the protests. Some critics have accused Columbia University of colluding with far-right groups in their response to the demonstrations. Amidst the unrest, Columbia University announced it would move classes online, while Harvard University closed its Yard in anticipation of further pro-Palestine protests. The protests have drawn attention to the university's handling of student activism and raised questions about the limits of free speech and the role of universities in addressing political issues.
